{"tid":1101523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(估國家）人有三急突噴「黃色物體」　x男完事繼續夾公仔","createTime":"2019-04-11T05:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T07:05:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9b6ba841aa3528ee9657e954adc2bf2c1e9b6b11","tid":1101523,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190410/photo/bkn-20190410204659179-0410_00952_001_01p.jpg?20190410224618\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190410%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190410204659179-0410_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20190410224618&h=35888e1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n台灣一名網民在Facebook上傳照片稱，台中一名男子周二（9日）帶兒子夾公仔時，疑人有三急，一抬腳就屙出滿地大便。其他網民都大鬧男子的舉動惡心，甚至稱隔住螢幕都有味。 <br />\n<br />\n文章指，男子當時雙眼緊盯着娃娃機台，突然右腳一抬，黃褐色的物體就從他褲管內跌出，之後又數度重複上述的動作。但驚人的是，男子似乎沒有離開的打算，繼續專心夾公仔。 <br />\n<br />\n事件引起熱議，僅數小時內留言就突破4000條，「有時間夾娃娃，為甚麼沒時間拉屎」、「是時候表演真正技術了，站着噴屎」、「褲子哪買的，竟然不被沾到」、「看起來不是第一次了，這抬腳的功夫」。"},{"pid":"187ecff54e14012711f508485e33941ed3c66683","tid":1101523,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:38:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190410/mobile/bkn-20190410204659179-0410_00952_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20190410%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190410204659179-0410_00952_001.html&d=KS%2FaBsiOfKbE8rejl7UGUiKjAP3shAOQj%2BHHIi00eAs%3D&h=178741f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20190410/mobile/bkn-20190410204659179-0410_00952_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"46c48d0da4a4090efcafbaf18e1b9ecb0ccd080e","tid":1101523,"uid":57928,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-11T05:39:00.000Z","msg":"原來台狗屙屎舉起右腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4c6ab75b15037339438d43c462b8e796840ef0","tid":1101523,"uid":132088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB